title: Stylist Sims
description:
This is a collection of all the \"donation\" files from Stylist Sims for The Sims 2.  No expansion packs are required for any of the sets, and collection files are included for each of them.  I have included pics for all of them as well.

Sets included are:  Barcelona Bath, Firenze Bedroom, Madrid Teenroom, Milano Kitchen, Montreal Living, Paris Kitchen and Toronto Living.
